features.text:
ABOUT THE SHOP

All Star Vintage is a clothing boutique based out of Tacoma Washington USA.

We curate vintage, music, and art events both in person and now in the Metaverse.


Please sign the guestbook while you are here if you are interested in making a purchase contact us on Twitter - @AllStarVintage

features.text: You’re invited to the inaugural Seattle World’s Vintage Fair! Meet us at the iconic Seattle Center to shop through 34,000 square feet of vintage clothing, collectibles, sneakers, accessories, records & other treasures. Enjoy activations from PNW brands, music, special guests, and activities. We’ll be celebrating a LEGENDARY birthday for a Seattle icon! Soo many more details to come! Curated by @throwbacksnw & @porvidanw / @tacomasundaymarket
Greg Cypher Captain of the Spaceship
